{"tid":1131222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球最大煙草集團Philip Morris進軍人壽保險行業 戒煙投保獲折扣","createTime":"2019-04-29T14:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T14:11:51.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1b104ceec769b40e6355ebd7f7ae66b8d6024f2f","tid":1131222,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/04/29/2123088_d232057b9b9243b5ad078bfa520b5f14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F04%2F29%2F2123088_d232057b9b9243b5ad078bfa520b5f14.png&h=af4ee553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全球最大煙草集團菲力浦莫里斯(Philip Morris，下稱PM)正進軍人壽保險行業。<br />\n<br />\nPM最近組建了全資子公司Reviti，計劃先於英國銷售人壽保險產品，未來將業務擴展至更多海外市場。吸煙者如果戒煙，或者改用電子煙等致癌性較低的產品，在投保時將可獲得折扣。<br />\n<br />\n根據PM的保險產品計劃，改用電子煙的投保者可以獲得2.5%的折扣，改用PM的電子煙產品3個月，則可獲得25%的折扣。至於成功戒煙至少一年的投保者，更可以獲得50%的折扣。<br />\n<br />\nPM行政總裁Andre Calantzopoulos早前表示，希望終有一日能夠徹底停止銷售傳統香煙。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2123088/Philip+Morris%E6%94%BB%E5%A3%BD%E9%9A%AA+%E6%88%92%E7%85%99%E6%8A%95%E4%BF%9D%E7%8D%B2%E6%8A%98%E6%89%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2123088%2FPhilip%2BMorris%25E6%2594%25BB%25E5%25A3%25BD%25E9%259A%25AA%2B%25E6%2588%2592%25E7%2585%2599%25E6%258A%2595%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%258A%2598%25E6%2589%25A3&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYluXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=facdac3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2123088/Philip+Morris%E6%94%BB%E5%A3%BD%E9%9A%AA+%E6%88%92%E7%85%99%E6%8A%95%E4%BF%9D%E7%8D%B2%E6%8A%98%E6%89%A3</a>"},{"pid":"71ca30610c78a7c0f963047b991799da58420548","tid":1131222,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:03:46.000Z","msg":"不如PM停售煙仔啦假仁假義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9